title: GTA Online: A Safehouse in the Hills
headline: GTA Online: A Safehouse in the Hills
subtitle: Missile Lock-on Jammer Now Available For Unweaponized Aircraft
content:
Improve your air defenses with the Missile Lock-On Jammer modification, which can now be added to several unweaponized aircraft in the Hangar Workshop.

This is also now available for all new vehicles (as well as several existing vehicles) via Imani Tech at your Agency Vehicle Workshop.

GTA+ Members can also access this mod at The Vinewood Club Garageâ€™s Vehicle Workshop and the Mansion Vehicle Workshop.

Eligible vehicles will include this upgrade in their website description.
